'''''Traveler, Find Truth Beyond the Illusion''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[Back to Earth in Evernight]].

==Steps==
# Return to your room to rest and wait for the Express to depart?
# Investigate the strange picture frame
# Head to the hall and figure out what's going on
# View Visitor Logs
# Answer the desk phone
# Investigate the phonograph message
# Confront the jellyfish left behind by Evernight
# Escape with Cyrene
# Talk with Cyrene
# Uncover your pre-awakening memories
# Escape with Sunday

